{"tid":708212,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【生存/建築/恐龍/多人遊戲】Steam Ark Survival Evolved大減價 仲唔買黎一齊玩","createTime":"2018-06-19T07:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T05:35:03.000Z","uid":127033,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4a02c62757c565b61c913775ff81644370c77b17","tid":708212,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:21:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Ark Survival Evolved</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/141745_1676bdf48cd5a7584843664b59fc0117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F141745_1676bdf48cd5a7584843664b59fc0117.jpg&h=57b9f440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實只係想多啲人一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻game一定要多人玩先生存到,所以依加只要係大部落,就唔怕比人打,甚至可以同圍打人.Game入面有好多個server,如果要打架,可以將玩緊既server啲野(物資/龍)傳送去人地server起據點,騎龍/揸槍/用炸藥攻人地既基地.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">【各種生物】</span></strong></span>識飛,陸地,海入面既都有<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/142127_eb6f6c53442b273444f8bd7aaa08800d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F142127_eb6f6c53442b273444f8bd7aaa08800d.jpg&h=9700e382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再詳細D <a href=\"http://www.dododex.com/dinosaurs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dododex.com%2Fdinosaurs&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=89595f2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dododex.com/dinosaurs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【馴養,繁殖,孵化,飼養】</span></strong></span><br />\n合作捉恐龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vbMe8WaE8BU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvbMe8WaE8BU&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=3bce8523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vbMe8WaE8BU</a><br />\n<br />\n獨角獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M7mis1qkUUc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM7mis1qkUUc&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=5f4d13dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M7mis1qkUUc</a><br />\n<br />\n養恐龍BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRPTZ0CZsn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTRPTZ0CZsn4&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=1c948056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRPTZ0CZsn4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【PVP】</span></strong></span>恐龍大個仔,當然要出去屠人地龍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (用既龍同上面條片唔同種)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=raMnFXn2f30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DraMnFXn2f30&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=97aa275d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=raMnFXn2f30</a><br />\n<br />\n打仗片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DtJuTk_T7sA&amp;t=174s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDtJuTk_T7sA%26t%3D174s&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d5007f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DtJuTk_T7sA&amp;t=174s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">【<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>基地建築</strong></span>】</span> 爆肝後既成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w5IAWlG1434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw5IAWlG1434&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9e525d85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w5IAWlG1434</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n減到100蚊咋,快點入手玩龍,對抗敵對部落啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/346110/ARK_Survival_Evolved/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F346110%2FARK_Survival_Evolved%2F&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=07aa01fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/346110/ARK_Survival_Evolved/</a>"},{"pid":"1b5c09e4627971bcc5914b6677bf5ae29bbee642","tid":708212,"uid":34162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"transfer data係咪一定要玩offical server先得? 我見出面d server有幾倍 咁玩完轉去人地到咪好爽"},{"pid":"2065c9c54ff8ec4893c98e88e2abbd0fccddc19c","tid":708212,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b5c09e4627971bcc5914b6677bf5ae29bbee642","tid":708212,"uid":34162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"transfer data係咪一定要玩offical server先得? 我見出面d server有幾倍 咁玩完轉去人地到咪好爽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:58:50.000Z","msg":"冇錯，得官服所有ser可以互通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  玩家開既都ser可以，但只限於同一個人開既server可傳,唔可以傳去人地開既。"},{"pid":"abfab4819084d06f956761994a605b03cea77d11","tid":708212,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:24:35.000Z","msg":"呢隻同VR ark park係